  - type: software
    title: "crs48/murmuration — TypeScript/Three.js Murmuration Simulation (Companion Project)"
    abstract: >
      Companion TypeScript/Three.js project providing 11 scenario presets,
      WebGL/WebGPU compute backends, 3D rendering with trail accumulation,
      adaptive quality system, threat/predator state machine, pilot/attractor
      system, environmental medium presets, and VR/WebXR support. Analyzed as
      a source of implementation patterns, parameter defaults, and roadmap
      priorities for the Python murmuration repository.
